<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 14:03:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>钙信号传导失调是唐氏综合症唾液分泌不足和微生物失调的基础</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/dysregulated-calcium-signaling-underlies-hyposalivation-and-microbial-dysbiosis-in-down-syndrome</link><description>患有唐氏综合症（DS）的人唾液流量减少，牙周疾病负担高。在 Dp16 小鼠（DS 模型）中，Son 等人。研究表明，唾液腺中钙信号传导不足是唾液分泌不足的基础，并与口腔和肠道微生物失调以及琥珀酸水平改变有关。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/dysregulated-calcium-signaling-underlies-hyposalivation-and-microbial-dysbiosis-in-down-syndrome2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 14:03:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/dysregulated-calcium-signaling-underlies-hyposalivation-and-microbial-dysbiosis-in-down-syndrome</guid></item><item><title>超越免疫抑制：自身免疫性疾病 T 细胞接合者的兴起杰弗里·琼斯博士</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/beyond-immunosuppression-the-rise-of-t-cell-engagers-for-autoimmune-disease-dr-jeffrey-jones</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 13:48:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/beyond-immunosuppression-the-rise-of-t-cell-engagers-for-autoimmune-disease-dr-jeffrey-jones</guid></item><item><title>在太空种植植物：未来月球和火星殖民地背后的科学马克·西奥托拉</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/growing-plants-in-space-the-science-behind-future-moon-and-mars-colonies-mark-ciotola</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 13:33:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/growing-plants-in-space-the-science-behind-future-moon-and-mars-colonies-mark-ciotola</guid></item><item><title>分层黑洞合并的证据越来越多</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/evidence-mounts-for-hierarchical-black-hole-mergers</link><description>对引力波观测的不同分析正在汇聚证据，证明通过反复合并产生的独特的大质量黑洞双星群。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/evidence-mounts-for-hierarchical-black-hole-mergers2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 13:18:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/evidence-mounts-for-hierarchical-black-hole-mergers</guid></item><item><title>反铁磁体的光写入指向新的存储设备和节能信息系统</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/optical-writing-of-antiferromagnets-points-toward-new-storage-devices-and-energy-efficient-information-systems</link><description>奥格斯堡大学参与的德日研究小组在反铁磁体的使用方面取得了重大突破。该团队首次成功仅使用超短激光脉冲写入磁信息，而不需要电流或磁场。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/optical-writing-of-antiferromagnets-points-toward-new-storage-devices-and-energy-efficient-information-systems.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 13:03:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/optical-writing-of-antiferromagnets-points-toward-new-storage-devices-and-energy-efficient-information-systems</guid></item><item><title>新型生物基聚合物表现出超越聚烯烃的优异拉伸性能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/new-biobased-polymers-exhibit-excellent-tensile-properties-beyond-polyolefins</link><description>东京都立大学Kotohiro Nomura教授的研究小组与大阪工业技术研究所的高级研究员Hiroshi Hirano和所长Seiji Higashi以及滋贺县大学的副教授Hiroki Takeshita的研究小组合作，从不可食用的生物可再生材料中开发出了生物基聚(酯酰胺)，该材料易于化学回收，并且在薄膜中表现出比商品塑料更好的机械(拉伸)性能。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-biobased-polymers-exhibit-excellent-tensile-properties-beyond-polyolefins2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 12:48:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/new-biobased-polymers-exhibit-excellent-tensile-properties-beyond-polyolefins</guid></item><item><title>人工智能系统将蛋白质序列翻译成文本，帮助揭示未知蛋白质的功能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/ai-system-translates-protein-sequences-into-text-helping-reveal-functions-of-unknown-proteins</link><description>在一篇论文中&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-system-translates-protein-sequences-into-text-helping-reveal-functions-of-unknown-proteins.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 12:33:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/ai-system-translates-protein-sequences-into-text-helping-reveal-functions-of-unknown-proteins</guid></item><item><title>新的人工智能插件可帮助开发人员自动化日常编程任务</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/new-ai-add-on-helps-developers-automate-everyday-programming-tasks</link><description>开发人员越来越依赖大型语言模型 (LLM) 来执行日常计算任务，例如修复错误、解释代码以及自动执行文本处理任务（例如过滤日志）。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-ai-add-on-helps-developers-automate-everyday-programming-tasks2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 12:18:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/new-ai-add-on-helps-developers-automate-everyday-programming-tasks</guid></item><item><title>发现原子“多米诺骨牌效应”驱动二维晶体中的相变</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/atomic-domino-effect-found-to-drive-phase-changes-in-a-two-dimensional-crystal</link><description>相变——材料从一种晶体结构转变为另一种晶体结构，从而获得截然不同的特性——在自然界中普遍存在。了解这些转变的微观机制对于控制材料特性和设计功能器件至关重要。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/atomic-domino-effect-found-to-drive-phase-changes-in-a-two-dimensional-crystal2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 12:03:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/atomic-domino-effect-found-to-drive-phase-changes-in-a-two-dimensional-crystal</guid></item><item><title>评论表明，视频游戏可能会适度提高你的记忆力和其他认知技能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/video-games-might-modestly-sharpen-your-memory-and-other-cognitive-skills-review-suggests</link><description>由于电子游戏是许多人日常生活的一部分，研究人员花了很多时间试图确定它们对大脑健康是否有益或有害。一项新研究， &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/video-games-might-modestly-sharpen-your-memory-and-other-cognitive-skills-review-suggests2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 11:48:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/video-games-might-modestly-sharpen-your-memory-and-other-cognitive-skills-review-suggests</guid></item></channel></rss>